{"tid":1517462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（830更新） twitter   @lam_chau_bar  如何認識外國twitter用家","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:46:57.000Z","uid":256966,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c1df4faf10d63297d3ea4ba761ac2b30e1859a84","tid":1517462,"uid":256966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係twitter入面的 @lam_chau_bar <br />\n<br />\n首先澄清：<span style=\"color: red;\">我不是連登入面的「我要攬炒」，但我全力支持連登的「我要攬炒」及其團隊。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post在此，今次唔講舊野了，請自己睇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（822更新）twitter (@lam_chau_bar)實戰經驗分享（歡迎起底睇返我的舊post）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1496781/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1496781/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n用twitter做外國文宣的，同我入哂黎，實戰經驗分享（歡迎起底睇返我係連登講twitter的post）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1488630/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1488630/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n（818）（twitter召集）唔好再留係同溫層<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1483314/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1483314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次講認識外國人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1）基本野，請  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名字</span></span>  和  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人簡介</span></span>  用英文<br />\n你唔用英文，外國人點睇得明？    睇唔明，點解要follow你？   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以繼續用中文出tweet 同返香港人講野，但係唔該 ，封面起碼係英文野先！<br />\n我由818  170萬人大遊行個日開始認真玩twitter，而家有呢個數字的follower，多謝返大家的信任，入面95％都係香港人的互follow，我地係香港區的twitter終於有返少少人氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDyk10D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDyk10D.png&h=2452993e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2）Follow返<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己的興趣</span></span> ，需要出post講下 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個人生活</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上個post講過，我決定行christian個人信仰的路線去進入外國人群體，而且信仰幫我走和理非路線，我開始去follow外國基督徒，同時入去佢地的post去comment（講日常生活野）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMOpKgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMOpKgt.jpg&h=274ed172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvb6XBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyvb6XBu.jpg&h=b1375a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjsYOJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjsYOJa.png&h=9df4e063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，開始有外國基督徒follow返我；我個twitter終於開始走向外國人的平台。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要抄我或者扮有信仰，只要做返你的興趣，follow返你的興趣，講返你的興趣，就會水到渠成，而且更開心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如，<span style=\"color: purple;\">攝影</span>的去交流影相；職業的講返職業；睇<span style=\"color: orange;\">nba</span>的，喂，美國人好鐘意nba架！！！<br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: gold;\">煮野食</span>的走女性twitter用家路線，多講飲食，然後係有沖突發生個日，post那些相片，請求佢地幫手轉發或者關注等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">旅行</span>都可以，假如你話最近沒有，咁你可以post返你以前的相片呀！ 既回味一下，又可以放鬆，同時connect到外國人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">個人生活</span>黎講，其實好簡單，<span style=\"color: purple;\">post下相，講下野就好</span>。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">要俾外國人都覺得，你不是高級文宣機器，你是活生生的香港人</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeH6dbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeH6dbV.jpg&h=9e2f29aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）進入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國人twitter</span></span>的路線<span style=\"color: red;\">（個人選擇）</span><br />\n因為黎緊<span style=\"color: red;\">9月美國國會復會</span>，就會傾<span style=\"color: red;\">《香港人權與民主法案》</span>。到時美國人會有更多news講香港，所以我定意要走去美國的twitter圈子裡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我基本上所有post都會用英文，務求令外國人睇得明。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為大家介紹一些<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國人常用short form</span>，然後考慮加係自己的簡介入面<br />\n#MAGA = Make America Great Again<br />\n#KAG = Keep America Great  （按照trump的講法，他已經帶領美國去great again，所以唔需要再去make，而係要去keep）<br />\n#Trump2020 = 美國2020大選，支持trump<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqOQEYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqOQEYF.png&h=21a0d586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國人都有<span style=\"color: red;\">兩極</span>，一面係<span style=\"color: red;\">支持trump</span>，一面係<span style=\"color: blue;\">反對trump</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我係twitter入面選擇了支持trump，</span>作為我的簡介和twitter定位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">大家可以揀either 支持 or 反對，務求令到香港人的聲音，係兩邊的美國群眾都能夠聽到</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如你進入 <span style=\"color: red;\">支持trump的定位，請你也留意</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCpPVyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCpPVyr.png&h=cb94b458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國人也有外國文宣組，有一個叫做 #Q 的美國twitter hashtag， 全寫係 #QAnon<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QAnon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FQAnon&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=ab865e33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QAnon</a><br />\n「Far right - alt right - nazi Conspiracy theory」<br />\n極簡單總結：有呢個 #Q 的人，就係表面上支持trump，實際上係反對trump的 twitter用家<br />\n唔好follow錯了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小總結： <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFsxTgc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFsxTgc.png&h=c93fad2f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n互相follow的人係少的，大概我每follow六個外國人，才會有一個人follow返我<br />\n所以，大家唔好灰心，盡力地進入外國人世界！<br />\n當你follower越來越多的時候，你出什麼post都會有人肯like和retweet；<br />\n當你有精品原創post的時候，大家都會願意like ＆ retweet<br />\n當你外國follower的基數都夠多的時候，那時，你的文宣就好大威力了。"},{"pid":"e836c3b8355f99e5019a92de0e0bd02a5d428a30","tid":1517462,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=d9c6876c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=b0c6d2c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=47c63f05\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"32a59f29070348087c89679b4cd3e463c3ee15bb","tid":1517462,"uid":256966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">小問答：推唔推trend和hashtag好呢？</span></strong><br />\n我有諗過上trend；但有資深twitter用家同過我講，trend嘅流動性好大，而且留返係香港自己的地區，又好似會變返圍爐取暖咁<br />\n去美國trend又唔夠人哋咁多人<br />\n<br />\n所以我個人就打消左呢個念頭， 轉為努力去識外國人，令佢哋都follow返我先，集中火力去搞好mutually follow foreigner in twitter<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCJX4uR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCJX4uR.jpg&h=95adaf85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nplease like &amp; retweet together.<br />\nTwitter is unlike facebook or ig. <br />\nIn facebook/ig, we tend to like.<br />\nIn twitter, people tend to retweet easily.<br />\nThis is twitter's culture.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔可以失去可信性！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1514722/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1514722/page/1</a><br />\n上次話警察掉氣油彈，全世界炒車，搞到連cnn都炒車和出信鄭重向香港警方道歉<br />\n請fact-Checked之後先至去retweet<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他twitter戰友研究識外國人的方法<br />\n－可以由Follow 同 comment 外國駐港記者啲tweets入手。再reply佢地tweet嘅comment嘅人<br />\n－我係政客d po add下面 留comment 既普通人<br />\n－反而我覺得唔使太多互add follow下黃之鋒 Donald trump pence果啲響果度亂add下 我另一個account add 到cnn問我拎source FYI<br />\n－係果d post 留comment係好大機會d外國人會回我地或者follow<br />\n－係呀 主動follow 佢地  唔一定要follow 名人 普通人其實仲好<br />\n－我自己就嘗試喺日本新聞留言，例如前日中國人喺大阪唱國歌嘅事都令唔少日本人出po討論，或者可以試下關注佢哋恐懼中共嘅諗法。平時出po Retweet都試下用幾種外文，希望幫到件事。<br />\n－Actually this is how you do it. Sorry I can&rsquo;t type it in Chinese. It&rsquo;s going to be in English. 1) you need language specific channels. One for English/French/Kieran/Japanese etc. Do not put them in the same channel. You can people who speak that language to be always engaged<br />\nEvery time you post something you tag it with all the protests #. Use different ones and scroll. so you can be on as many channel # Once you have established your twitter account. Say with 15 posts, start adding and liking to people in your language group you think may be<br />\nInterested in the Hong Kong Democratic movement. Make sure you don&rsquo;t look like a bot. Add some personal commentary, not just retweets. People block bots<br />\nThen you know, you just to keep doing it until you get a following. Don&rsquo;t be discouraged. It takes time. And even if you only have ten people see it. Then it&rsquo;s ten people more than yesterday. Add oil."},{"pid":"ef7e7d6a901733832351b73f4b240fc5f019bc02","tid":1517462,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"cc9e059278d294781c34d760b607b3f41a80c43f","tid":1517462,"uid":126622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"見到有外國人出左個活動tag叫 #FollowBackHongKong<br />\n<br />\n佢地話見到就會follow你班新用家關注香港既野"},{"pid":"1853d8bcd1df8fcf853a99166902b337ecf8a0ad","tid":1517462,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0139ea96671ccfb8969603cd9efa6fa093e7d8f","tid":1517462,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7e1b065542acf13aab8a166ecd18e06f5c951ea","tid":1517462,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0063ee92af4f039cf27145299e0416240be5b0fa","tid":1517462,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"Push! <br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11945a5697bba7ba3cdd1f3c2131ed5b5ae4aee8","tid":1517462,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"649ace217b0fef3946e40b1edc96bdf53267310b","tid":1517462,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db0ee3e7a712f59fd40ceb92af7bd168c2bdceec","tid":1517462,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800273cf354253879102d0ad9ffe2cae9026145","tid":1517462,"uid":256966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"關於 #Q （匿名者Q）  的補充<br />\n<br />\n//匿名者Q理論支持者認為，美國一直以來被一個由極少數人士控制着的「深層政府」（Deep State）所劫持，而總統特朗普正在與其戰鬥，希望擺脫這個權力核心的操縱。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因此，匿名者Q認為美國人必須支持特朗普，瓦解「深層政府」的重大陰謀，特朗普也曾直指「深層政府」是對美國民主制度的一個重大威脅。</span></span>//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/世界說/255119/中期選舉-深層政府-暗裏操控特朗普-一場美國政治大陰謀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA%2F255119%2F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E6%B7%B1%E5%B1%A4%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%9A%97%E8%A3%8F%E6%93%8D%E6%8E%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8hSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=46951ad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/世界說/255119/中期選舉-深層政府-暗裏操控特朗普-一場美國政治大陰謀</a><br />\n<br />\n所以，#Q 目前根據維基百科和上述文章，可以咁樣理解：<br />\n用#Q的tag的人，係最支持trump，支持到覺得trump係「美國唯一拯救」的地步。<br />\n目前美國twitter，#Q ／#QAnon  的用家是有的，但係討厭呢個hashtag的人都有很多。<br />\n<br />\n#WWG1WGA, signifying the motto &quot;where we go one, we go all.&quot;<br />\n「#WWG1WGA」呢個都係 #QAnon 的支持者會用的tag"},{"pid":"b3d767e11e9b3b8a29e620f31c9cf9735cd43f59","tid":1517462,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b398ab6faa1dde1a1835e4ed52650129a6ddf7e6","tid":1517462,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd68334be21a25559ec8429478cea5a420dd0aa0","tid":1517462,"uid":6311